@startuml
!define AWSPUML https://raw.githubusercontent.com/awslabs/aws-icons-for-plantuml/v14.0/dist
!include AWSPUML/AWSCommon.puml

title Coverage Robot - Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "GitHub App" as GitHub
participant "API Service\n(Lambda)" as API
participant "Cognito" as Cognito
participant "S3" as S3
participant "SQS" as SQS
participant "EventBridge" as EventBridge
participant "Orchestrator Service\n(Lambda)" as Orchestrator
participant "Event Store\n(DynamoDB)" as EventStore
participant "Ingest Service\n(Lambda)" as Ingest
participant "Analyse Service\n(Lambda)" as Analyse
participant "BigQuery" as BigQuery
participant "Publish Service\n(Lambda)" as Publish
participant "Configuration\n(DynamoDB)" as Config
participant "CloudWatch EMF" as CloudWatch

== Upload Coverage Report Flow ==

User -> API: Request upload URL
activate API
API -> Cognito: Validate upload token
activate Cognito
Cognito --> API: Token validated
deactivate Cognito
API -> S3: Generate pre-signed URL
activate S3
S3 --> API: Pre-signed URL
deactivate S3
API --> User: Return pre-signed URL
deactivate API

User -> S3: Upload coverage data
activate S3
S3 --> User: Upload complete
deactivate S3

User -> API: Notify upload complete
activate API
API -> SQS: Enqueue upload message
activate SQS
SQS --> API: Message queued
deactivate SQS
API --> User: Acknowledged
deactivate API

== Webhook Processing Flow ==

GitHub -> API: Webhook event (PR/Push)
activate API
API -> API: Validate webhook signature
API -> SQS: Enqueue webhook message
activate SQS
SQS --> API: Message queued
deactivate SQS
API --> GitHub: Webhook acknowledged
deactivate API

== Event-Driven Orchestration Flow ==

SQS -> Orchestrator: Pull message
activate Orchestrator
Orchestrator -> EventStore: Check event state
activate EventStore
EventStore --> Orchestrator: Current state
deactivate EventStore

Orchestrator -> EventStore: Persist state change
activate EventStore
EventStore --> Orchestrator: State persisted
deactivate EventStore

Orchestrator -> EventBridge: Publish event
activate EventBridge
EventBridge --> Orchestrator: Event published
deactivate EventBridge

Orchestrator -> CloudWatch: Report metrics
activate CloudWatch
CloudWatch --> Orchestrator: Metrics recorded
deactivate CloudWatch
deactivate Orchestrator

== Ingest Event Processing ==

EventBridge -> Ingest: Ingest event
activate Ingest
Ingest -> S3: Fetch coverage data
activate S3
S3 --> Ingest: Coverage data
deactivate S3

Ingest -> Ingest: Process coverage data
Ingest -> BigQuery: Store aggregated data
activate BigQuery
BigQuery --> Ingest: Data stored
deactivate BigQuery

Ingest -> EventStore: Update event state
activate EventStore
EventStore --> Ingest: State updated
deactivate EventStore

Ingest -> EventBridge: Publish ingest complete event
activate EventBridge
EventBridge --> Ingest: Event published
deactivate EventBridge

Ingest -> CloudWatch: Report metrics
activate CloudWatch
CloudWatch --> Ingest: Metrics recorded
deactivate CloudWatch
deactivate Ingest

== Analysis Flow ==

EventBridge -> Analyse: Analyse event
activate Analyse
Analyse -> Config: Fetch project configuration
activate Config
Config --> Analyse: Configuration data
deactivate Config

Analyse -> S3: Fetch current coverage data
activate S3
S3 --> Analyse: Current coverage
deactivate S3

Analyse -> BigQuery: Query historical coverage
activate BigQuery
BigQuery --> Analyse: Historical data
deactivate BigQuery

Analyse -> Analyse: Calculate coverage metrics\n(with caching)
Analyse -> Analyse: Compare with previous state
Analyse -> Analyse: Generate coverage report

Analyse -> EventStore: Update event state
activate EventStore
EventStore --> Analyse: State updated
deactivate EventStore

Analyse -> EventBridge: Publish analysis complete event
activate EventBridge
EventBridge --> Analyse: Event published
deactivate EventBridge

Analyse -> CloudWatch: Report metrics
activate CloudWatch
CloudWatch --> Analyse: Metrics recorded
deactivate CloudWatch
deactivate Analyse

== Publish Flow ==

EventBridge -> Publish: Publish event
activate Publish
Publish -> EventStore: Fetch analysis results
activate EventStore
EventStore --> Publish: Analysis data
deactivate EventStore

Publish -> Config: Fetch configuration\n(comment style, path replacements)
activate Config
Config --> Publish: Configuration data
deactivate Config

Publish -> Publish: Format coverage report

Publish -> GitHub: Post coverage comment on PR
activate GitHub
GitHub --> Publish: Comment posted
deactivate GitHub

Publish -> EventStore: Update event state (complete)
activate EventStore
EventStore --> Publish: State updated
deactivate EventStore

Publish -> CloudWatch: Report metrics
activate CloudWatch
CloudWatch --> Publish: Metrics recorded
deactivate CloudWatch
deactivate Publish

== Badge Generation Flow ==

User -> API: Request coverage badge
activate API
API -> Config: Fetch badge data from DynamoDB
activate Config
Config --> API: Coverage percentage
deactivate Config

API -> API: Generate SVG badge
API --> User: Return badge SVG
deactivate API

@enduml
